EX–5 EX–5 "Straw Hat Theatre #5: Monster Time"Transliteration: "Mugiwara Gekijō Sono Go Monster Time" (Japanese:麦わら劇場その5「Monster Time」) N/A N/A October 29, 2006(2006-10-29)[n 8] January 11, 2015

In the town of Monsuton(モンストン), thegorgonRojūsa(ロジューサ)has lost her favorite earrings. To cheer her up, her friends, thedragonLugyao(ルギヤオ), thecentaurUsoppaka(ウソッパカ), thekrakenChopāken(チョパーケン), themermaidSutoronamī(ストロナミー),  thekappaSanzarā(サンザラー), and theminotaurZoromiruku(ゾロミルク), try to find her something better.[30]
